  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 39751187402752
    m_Localized: Iroha's emergency food.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 39751250317312
    m_Localized: Koyori's pet coyote robot.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 39751250317313
    m_Localized: Chloe's very ferocious killer whale.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 39751250317314
    m_Localized: 'An umbrella octopus with a chewy appearance.


      Launch a powerful
      angel ring laser forward.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 39751250317315
    m_Localized: 'Sora''s powerful teddy bear.


      Hold the unit tight and stuns.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 39751250317316
    m_Localized: 'A creature like a marshmallow with horns.


      Send out soul
      beads to damage.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 39751254511616
    m_Localized: 'The bodyguard of the holoX.


      Pattern 1 - Flys a powerful
      sword wind forward.

      Pattern 2 - After taking a ready position, cut down
      the unit in front and stuns. If there are no units in the range, move forward
      by 3 blocks.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 39751254511617
    m_Localized: 'The scientist of the holoX.


      Pattern 1 - Koyori bursts 5
      pre-buried landmines in front.

      Pattern 2 - Throw 2 poison potions at
      the random tiles. Sometimes accidentally throws the recovery pills she was
      trying to use for emergency.

      Pattern 3 - stuns 1 random unit regardless
      of distance.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 39751254511618
    m_Localized: "The cleaner of the holoX.\n\nPattern 1 - Throw 1 dagger forward.\nPattern
      2 \u2013 Cloe crouches down and quickly disappears. She then performs a \"Flash
      Strike\" on three random rows.\nPattern 3 - Cloe disappears into the dark.
      After this, it appears to 1 random unit and causes fatal damage."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 15609584629026816
    m_Localized: These are Ganmo's little friends. Unlike what they look like, they
      can't lay bomb eggs.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 15609584712912896
    m_Localized: 'The executive officer of the holoX.


      Pattern 1 - Ganmo moves
      independently. It flies forward and, damages units in its path.

      Pattern
      2 - Lui spells a ''magic wave'' in front. After this, she fires ''magic bolt''
      in the cross direction, and once again in the x direction.

      Pattern 3
      - Lui designates a random unit and spells ''blood drain''. it damages targeted
      unit and drops ''blooddrop'' object. ''blooddrop'' restores HP and disappears
      a monster or unit on the same tile.

      Pattern 4 - Lui spells a ''magic
      explosion'' on all tiles except the safe zone.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 35904632197189632
    m_Localized: "The leader of the holoX who founded it.\n\nLaplus casts 3 random
      patterns in each phase. After a phase ends, Laplus enters a groggy state. \nDuring
      the phase, Laplus takes only 30% of the total damage, but during the groggy
      state, Laplus takes 150% of the damage. \nEach time a unit retires, Laplus's
      death count increases by 1. After the groggy state ends, Laplus deals damage
      directly to their main HP equal to 30 times the death count.\n\nPattern 1 -
      Laplus designates a random unit periodically and summons \"Dimensional Shard.\"
      The Dimensional Shard will explode after 10 seconds, dealing damage to the
      target unit. Allied units can destroy the shard before it explodes to prevent
      damage.\nPattern 2 - Laplus casts \"Doom Laser\" on all rows.\nPattern 3 -
      Laplus summons \"Order Tiles\" corresponding to the number of units. After
      a certain time, any unit not on its designated tile will be killed. This pattern
      repeats three times.\nPattern 4 - Laplus summons a \"Black Hole\" that chases
      units. The Black Hole deals random damage between 1% and 100%.\nPattern 5 -
      Laplus casts \"Massive Dimensional Collapse\" on all tiles.\nPattern 6 - Laplus
      casts \"Hand of Magic\" three times, followed by an X-shaped \"Doom Laser.\""
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 50764120959979520
    m_Localized: Miko's divine beast. Its tail is hidden behind its somehow unusual
      large body.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76447203864317952
    m_Localized: Karas, a longtime friend of Laplace.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76447203906260992
    m_Localized: "A chubby cat with a Hexagram pin on head.\n\nPattern 1 \u2013 Casts
      'Lightning Magic' on a random tile to deal damage."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76447203906260993
    m_Localized: "A small battery robot of Roboco.\n\nPattern 1 \u2013 Teleports
      forward by 2 tiles."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  references:
    version: 2
